---
title: Beef and Veggie Meatballs with Cucumber Salad and Spaghetti
description: A simple, wholesome dinner for everyone to enjoy - you can’t go wrong with this delicious meatball and wheat spaghetti recipe. Packing a serious flavour punch, our meatballs are a delicious combination of beef mince, grated courgette, carrot and Italian herbs. Served in a simple tomato sauce alongside a chopped salad to keep the flavours fresh, make this recipe your go-to for cosy nights in.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-and-veggie-meatballs-8bdec8ad-b638dced.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/beef-and-veggie-meatballs-5c362316e3f3396b414e4722-a5c41b33.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/beef-and-veggie-meatballs-5c362316e3f3396b414e4722
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 830 kcal
  fat: 12 g
  saturated fat: 5 g
  carbohydrates: 133 g
  sugar: 31 g
  protein: 43 g
  sodium: 3 g
  serving size: 724
cuisine: Italian
